snippet.description:
NCT 127, debuted in July 2016, is NCTâ€™s Seoul Team and the number â€˜127â€™ is the longitude of Seoul, symbolizing the groupâ€™s home base, the home of K-pop, as they continue to actively promote all across the world.

The group is known for their impressive stage performances and trendy music, releasing hit songs like Kick It, Punch, Superhuman, Highway to Heaven, Regular, and Cherry Bomb. NCT 127's 2nd full-length album, 'NCT #127 Neo Zone' debuted at No.5 on the Billboard 200 and No.2 on Billboard's Artist 100 chart in addition to landing the No.1 spot on 4 charts total including Billboardâ€™s Top Album Sales, Top Current Album Sales, World Albums and Tastemaker Albums chart, further proving their popularity as worldwide superstars.
